"。你需要找到能读懂这段文字的人，才能施行其中的仪式。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3766
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/text"
msgstr "（启蒙船员）让你的启蒙船员誊写这段文字。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3768
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的启蒙船员为你写下了一套密文。借助它，你得以理解这段文字所记载的内容：两种"
"仪式；一种能让启蒙者从单纯的信徒身份升华，成为黑暗之神的选者之一，另一种则能"
"让你获取一份独属于启蒙者的机械类馈赠。\n"
"\n"
"这些仪式的末尾夹着一张松散的书页——上面的字迹比其他部分潦草得多。事实上，其笔"
"迹看上去完全不同，并且记载了另一个独立的仪式……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3772
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "调查神眷奉献仪式。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3774
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"神眷奉献仪式：\n"
"该仪式会为你提供一艘属于黑暗神选者的舰船位置，你必须在战斗中将其击败以证明自"
"身价值。完成此举可让你的一名启蒙信徒成为黑暗神选者。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3777
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_CREW_DDENLIGHTENED\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
