msgstr "你的天选船员为你写下了一套密文。借助它，你得以理解：天选者能够以人类献祭为媒"
"介，定位他们的敌人——那些与黑暗之神为敌的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3830
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[@req=\"dddeepone_chosen\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
