msgstr "调查电蓝色文字——风暴之兆。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3908
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"虽然你无法读懂这段文字，但这一部分的图示展示出你只能推测为雷暴的景象，以及操"
"控这些雷暴的奇异存在。你需要找到能读懂这段文字的人，才能施行其中的仪式。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3910
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTEMPEST_ALIGNED\"]/text"
msgstr "（风暴船员）让你麾下效忠风暴的船员誊写这段文字。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3912
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTEMPEST_ALIGNED\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你麾下效忠风暴的船员触碰这本典籍，相关文字瞬间变得清晰可读。你得以明白，风暴"
"教派借助这些仪式向风暴证明自身虔诚，并以此换取风暴的子嗣。\n"
"\n"
"在这些仪式的末尾，夹着一张散页——上面的字迹比其他部分潦草得多，笔迹也截然不同"
"，记载着一个独立的仪式……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3916
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTEMPEST_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "调查唤风仪式。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3918
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTEMPEST_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"唤风仪式：\n"
"该仪式会根据你的意愿，将一名风暴子嗣或风暴守卫召唤至你所在的房间。风暴守卫无"
"需额外代价即可被奴役，但奴役风暴子嗣需要额外献祭1—2名人类。若无法满足其对血肉"
"的需求，仪式将会失败，子嗣也会转为敌对。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3921
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTEMPEST_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "有意思。合上这本书。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3927
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTEMPEST_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "调查那张松散的书页。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3929
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTEMPEST_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这一页并未按惯例描述仪式的本质与流程，反而更像是一段独白，或是被撕下来的摘录"
"。内容如下：\n"
"\n"
"“这下才叫奇迹嘛！依我看，就是这种漂亮又文艺的故事，最早让那位大人物对你这么上"
"心，伊芙。呃……算了。我……就当我没说过，行不？反正我知道你也不会看这些，但我也"
"清楚，你对过去的自己特别敏感。”\n"
"\n"
"“听着，我本来就不擅长说漂亮话，也不擅长画这些图，但是……我答应过你，就一定会做"
"到。你信任我，就像我信任你一样。如果非得画这些奇怪又文艺的植物才行，那我就画"
"！”\n"
"\n"
"文字到此结束。后面是几张画得很粗糙的图示，大致画出了仪式步骤，还有一些类似藤"
"蔓、植物状生物的涂鸦。不过在这些拙劣的图画旁，特意强调画出了十几把匕首和其他"
"刃具……你只能推测，无论这个仪式是什么，都必须做好战斗的准备。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3937
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTEMPEST_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "奇怪。合上这本书。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3943
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTEMPEST_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "算了。合上这本书。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3949
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "合上这本书。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3955
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[7]/text"
msgstr "调查那片刺目的白色文字——新生教令。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3957
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[7]/event/text"
msgstr "虽然你无法读懂这段文字，但这一部分的图示展示出无数道闪电，包裹着一副空铠甲。"
"你需要找到能读懂这段文字的人，才能施行其中的仪式。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3959
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/text"
msgstr "（终焉装甲）让终焉装甲誊写这段文字。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3961
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/event/text"
msgstr "终焉装甲的核心闪烁光芒，你忽然能够读懂眼前的文字。你可以施行这个仪式，以风暴"
"之名建立教派，从而换取它的恩惠。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3963
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "调查风暴扩张仪式。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3965
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"风暴扩张仪式：\n"
"该仪式会为你指明一处关键地点，你可以在那里召唤一艘隶属于风暴教派的舰船。他们"
"会从该地开始扩张影响力，但需要物资供给。你为他们提供物资，风暴便会赐予你随机"
"恩惠，并强化对你舰船的祝福。提供的物资越多，获得高品质恩惠的概率越高。恩惠分"
"为三个品质：普通、高阶与寰宇。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3968
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "调查风暴祝福的效果。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3970
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"风暴祝福效果：\n"
"1级：6点生命值能量护盾，受影响的无人机与效忠风暴的船员可提供并汲取1点能量，同"
"时移动与维修速度提升至1.2倍，战斗与破坏伤害提升至1.1倍。\n"
"\n"
"2级：9点生命值能量护盾，受影响的无人机与效忠风暴的船员可提供并汲取1点能量，同"
"时移动与维修速度提升至1.4倍，战斗与破坏伤害提升至1.2倍。\n"
"\n"
"3级：12点生命值能量护盾，受影响的无人机与效忠风暴的船员可提供并汲取1点能量，"
"同时移动与维修速度提升至1.6倍，战斗与破坏伤害提升至1.3倍。\n"
"\n"
"4级：15点生命值能量护盾，受影响的无人机与效忠风暴的船员可提供并汲取2点能量，"
"同时移动与维修速度提升至1.8倍，战斗与破坏伤害提升至1.4倍。\n"
"\n"
"5级：18点生命值能量护盾，受影响的无人机与效忠风暴的船员可提供并汲取2点能量，"
"同时移动与维修速度提升至2.0倍，战斗与破坏伤害提升至1.5倍。\n"
"\n"
"6级：21点生命值能量护盾，受影响的无人机与效忠风暴的船员可提供并汲取2点能量，"
"同时移动与维修速度提升至2.2倍，战斗与破坏伤害提升至1.6倍，并获得穿越门体的相"
"位移动能力。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:3983
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[7]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
