"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[8]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[3]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "有意思。合上这本书。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4044
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[8]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "调查魂缚仪式。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4046
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[8]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"魂缚仪式：\n"
"该仪式会为你标出距离最近的灵魂瘟疫母体位置，你可以尝试将其束缚为你所用。执行"
"此仪式时，母体会动用它所能支配的所有灵魂对你发动攻击；你必须在灵魂瘟疫躯壳与"
"躯壳编织者的一波波侵袭中存活下来。若能挺过这场攻击，你便可将母体束缚为你效力"
"，它会在你今后要求的任何战斗中前来支援。你必须已为灵魂瘟疫仪式完成至少三次献"
"祭，才能施展该仪式，且该仪式仅可进行一次。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4049
