#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4182
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[9]/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "合上这本书。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4188
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[10]/text"
msgstr "查阅这段漆黑的文字，神秘学初学者指南。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4190
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[10]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你意识到你竟然能读懂这一部分……它似乎概述了几种基础仪式，并详细说明了仪式的通"
"用要求和规则。\n"
"\n"
"在这些仪式和规则的末尾，夹着一张松散的书页——上面的文字比其他部分潦草得多。的"
"确，它的笔迹看起来完全不同……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4194
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[10]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "调查仪式的要求与规则。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4196
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[10]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"规则如下：\n"
"规则1：仪式必须在光速航行时进行。\n"
"规则2：除狩猎仪式外，所有仪式均需要活人献祭。\n"
"规则3：首次献祭时，若没有活人可供献祭，可使用大量垃圾作为替代品（100废料）。"
"\n"
"规则4：特定仪式需要特定的追随者，以及对黑暗之神之道的相应理解。\n"
"规则5：仪式未能完成通常不会有惩罚，但献祭的物品不会返还。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4204
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[10]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4206
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[10]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"规则6：某些仪式只有在满足先决条件后才可进行。\n"
"规则7：若你在执行仪式后调整航径，因此产生的任何任务都会丢失。\n"
"规则8：若你既想执行仪式又想与某位管理者交谈，必须先查看其任务并使用跃迁速度增"
"强部件。\n"
