"这段内容描述了向黑暗之神奉献所能获得的益处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4384
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDDARKEST_GAZE\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
