#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4386
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDDARKEST_GAZE\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"奉献分为三个等级。每个等级都能让你通过为时序系统供能，获得更强的效果。时序系"
"统中激活的每一级能量都会使收益按倍数提升（1倍→2倍→3倍），但这些收益的上限由你"
"的奉献等级决定。除超级护盾外，所有收益都需要时序系统处于供能状态。你的奉献等"
"级可通过仪式提升，该过程需要献祭。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4388
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DARKGOD_CURSED_BOOK\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDDARKEST_GAZE\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
