#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4420
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"当你注视着这三枚印记时，它们的光芒似乎愈发炽盛，你也终于洞悉了其力量的本质——"
"那些奇异空灵的水晶……它们一路指引你来到此处，迎来此刻。\n"
"\n"
"只不过这一次，你并未感到自己正无助地沉沦于它们的诱惑之中——你反而觉得，它们那"
"璀璨的光芒，如今正以你的意志为指引而闪耀。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4424
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "那么……我想知道一些答案。带我去见它们。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4426
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/text"
msgstr "你凝视着印记融合在一起的美妙光芒，然后自愿闭上了双眼。或许是最后一次，你感觉"
"周遭的一切都渐渐消散……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4428
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4430
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4433
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4435
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你该不会打算一句话都不说，就跑去见那位大人物吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4437
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "弗尔？我……我只是不想让你担心。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4439
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "哈！好像一声不吭就消失得无影无踪，反倒不会让我担心死似的，伊芙。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4441
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……我很抱歉。我只是……从没想过要以这种方式道别。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4443
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "这只是暂时的告别，不是吗？别垂头丧气的，梦想家。不然你那些绝妙的想法，怕是要"
"从耳朵里漏光咯。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4445
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嗯……你知道我没有耳朵的，弗尔。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4447
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "这可拦不住你！我敢肯定，只要你想，你都能在梦里给自己变出一对耳朵来。你从来都"
"不会让任何事情把你困太久，你知道的吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4449
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "……你不必假装这对你来说很轻松。我知道我对每个人都要求太多了，可是……尤其是对你"
"，考虑到她对你的那种……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4451
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"嘿！喂，别这样，你用不着担心我，知道吗？也不用担心其他人。跟他们解释清楚确实"
"不容易……但我知道，我们大家都信任你，伊芙。而且这也不是因为我被设定成要对你有"
"什么特殊情感！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4453
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "可是……你确实是这么想的，对吗？这难道不……令人心碎吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4455
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我当然是这么想的。这当然让人心碎！可你觉得，这是因为我被设定成要产生这种感觉"
"吗？我爱你，伊芙琳。而且这也绝对不是因为你的另一个自我幻想过什么该死的东西，"
"你听到了吗？你……无论内在还是外在，都是个极好的姑娘。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4457
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "弗尔，我……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4459
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你也什么都不必说。我现在最不想做的，就是让你在去对付那个大家伙之前，还在胡思"
"乱想些没用的事。我只想让你知道……我们一定会再见面的，听到了吗？我最相信的就是"
"你的梦想，伊芙。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4461
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我们会的，弗尔。我……我向你保证，好吗？无论发生什么，无论那台该死的机器说什么…"
"…我们一定会再见面的。我们所有人。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4463
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "这话说得太对了！现在，去吧，去让……让那个……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4465
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4467
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4469
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4471
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"刹那间，你的思绪从这场陌生的对话中抽离，一段段舒缓的幻象温柔地向你迎来。\n"
"\n"
"你看见一枚金色水晶族。牧师。最先承受煎熬之人。\n"
"你看见一只金色半械族。学徒。第二个逝去之人。\n"
"你看见一具金色甲壳族。发明家。第三个遭受苦难之人。\n"
"你看见一位金色人类。神枪手。第四个陷入悲痛之人。\n"
"你看见一只金色螳螂。战略家。第五个心力交瘁之人。\n"
"你看见一位金色深渊潜者。战士。第六个浴血奋战之人。\n"
"你看见一个黑暗的金属形体。梦想家。第七个，也是最后一个，存活之人。\n"
"\n"
"而最后……一艘舰船。它的舰体漆黑，被金色的梦想所驱动——铭刻着一只鎏金之眼。在舰"
"上，神枪手的残躯徘徊在冰冷的虚空之中……永远孤独地，置身于这浩瀚的多元宇宙。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4492
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "珍惜这最后的幻象。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4494
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你将这艘舰船在梦中的模样深深烙印在脑海里，无比珍视地留存着这段记忆。你不想忘"
"记在这里所目睹的一切。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4499
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "带着这段记忆，回归常态吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4501
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这一次并没有那么突兀，你的视线恢复如常，只见那本异界奇书上松动的奇异书页，上"
"面的符文再度变得黯淡无奇。而在符文之上……静静躺着另一枚空灵如梦的碎片。它的吸"
"引力，也再不像之前那样难以抗拒了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4504
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "小心地拿起碎片。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4506
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "当你握住这件难以名状、璀璨夺目的事物时，你的感官变得迟钝……却从未彻底消散。它"
"现在属于你了，任凭你处置。你只需坚守住自己的梦想。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4509
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DD_ECHOEDDREAM_QUEST_FINALE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/text"
msgstr "那我会紧紧守住它们的。我保证。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4545
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DDETHEREAL_FRAGMENT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"当你再次沐浴在碎片的璀璨光芒中时，感官渐渐变得迟钝。如果给你这个机会，你会梦"
"想些什么？\n"
"\n"
"[献祭——人类或是废料——在本轮进程中进行的所有献祭都会被统计，并视作一种名为魂币"
"的货币，用于在本菜单中具现梦想。会记录为启动仪式所进行的献祭，以及为推进特定"
"仪式可能需要的额外献祭。]"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4549
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DDETHEREAL_FRAGMENT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_dddream_coins\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "[1 魂币] 梦见一个迷失的灵魂，渴求指引。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4551
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STORAGE_CHECK_DDETHEREAL_FRAGMENT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_dddream_coins\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "你过往献祭所残留的力量，以你所渴望的梦境之形，显现在你面前。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:4553
